                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4486" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">PJMT-0086</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9897 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国有企业再出发： EPC工程管理的初尝试</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The New Stage of State-owned Enterprises: The First Attempt of EPC Project Management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王宁，聂鑫，张典</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国能源建设集团东北电力第二工程有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPC工程；文化冲突；工程管理；跨国合作</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPC Project；Cultural Conflicts, Engineering Management,Transnational cooperation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">DC公司是一家从事电力建设的老牌国有企业，其公司领导层在国家“一带一路”倡议的指引下，决定向海外尤其是欠发达地区拓展业务。然而，进军国际市场并非易事，国际项目不仅对工程的技术和质量要求严格，同时由于组成结构的复杂性以及团队成员的多元化，其对总承包商的综合管理能力也提出了更高的挑战。在第一次异国项目的实施中，文化冲突给DC公司带来了重重阻碍，也让其承受了前所未有的项目执行压力。本案例选取了3个DC公司在B国实际项目执行过程中遇到的文化冲突情景，帮助学生了解大型海外工程项目管理中的常见问题，通过学习相关理论，掌握缓和文化冲突、增强管理能力的解决措施，最终推动中国企业在国际市场中得到纵深发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">DC is a veteran state-owned enterprise engaged in power construction. Under the guidance of the national initiative “Belt and Road”, the company’s leadership decided to expand its overseas business, especially in less developed areas. However, it is not easy to enter the international market. International projects not only have strict technical and quality requirements for the project, but due to the complexity of the composition structure and the diversity of team members, it also pose a higher challenge to the general contractor&#39;s comprehensive management ability. In the implementation of the first foreign project, the cultural conflict has brought many obstacles to DC company, which also make DC company suffer unprecedented project execution pressure. This case selects three cultural conflict scenarios encountered by the DC companies in the actual project implementation process in Country B, helping students understand common problems in the management of large-scale overseas engineering projects , learn the relevant theoretical methods,  master the solutions to mitigate cultural conflicts, and enhance management capabilities, ultimately promoting Chinese enterprises get further development in the international market.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《管理沟通》、《跨文化管理》、《管理学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化冲突理论；组织管理；质量管理；进度管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-05</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
